data.title: Carroll Maryland Map
data.text:
Here is the map for Carroll County located in Maryland. Click on the map to get specific details on the Carroll community, driving directions for Carroll County, and to get an enlarged Carroll Maryland map.

Some of the primary cities, towns, and communities in Carroll County are: Westminster, Eldersburg, Hampstead, Manchester, Taneytown, Sykesville, New Windsor, Union Bridge, and Mount Airy.

The Carroll County Government offices are located in Westminster, MD. Carroll County is within the Baltimore and Washington metro area. Carroll County is bordered by Baltimore County, Howard County, Frederick County, York County PA, and Adams County PA.

The population of Carroll County MD is 167,134 according to the 2010 census.
